{"tid":1394740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇請各大公司容許員工8月5號Home Office/ 彈性上班","createTime":"2019-08-01T13:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T00:47:42.000Z","uid":13781,"like":86,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9943456e2b4fec75862045b1ea9009c27c04c8","tid":1394740,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"今日同個job agent傾開<br />\n佢地公司MD今日已經出左email話8月5號員工可以Home Office<br />\n理由係會預視到交通大擠塞同顧及員工人身安全<br />\n仲話佢唔少客內部都傾緊甚至宣佈可以Home Office<br />\n<br />\n所以如果你已經係公司HR／中層<br />\n不妨聽日用呢兩個理由遊說高層Home Office<br />\n多一間大公司、多一條team肯比員工Home Office<br />\n8月5號就多啲人出黎集會<br />\n講真，Home Office進可攻、退可守<br />\n唔洗員工十五十六之餘又嬴到佢地尊敬<br />\nagent話個個一收到email都好appreciate<br />\n<br />\n可能你問<br />\n陣間公司真係叫你星期一係屋企登入system、或比野你返去跟<br />\n咪無左罷工意義<br />\n小弟愚見<br />\n電腦野咪話唔知點解登入唔到<br />\n有野跟weekend快手快腳清左佢<br />\n罷工意義就係星期一七區遍地開花<br />\n夠人就有noise<br />\n<br />\n如果各位大家覺得make sense<br />\n推推上熱門<br />\n推埋上報<br />\n幫公司高層聽日落決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4546025f1f4326f941b64eb493d46d33227dece","tid":1394740,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"55965268e9aecc1f52e0e22c467d412fcb27393e","tid":1394740,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"f9bd3371492b25807ecdeba0926b51f1e7316a80","tid":1394740,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"缺一不"},{"pid":"302de71a291e4431aad052d32df28be62a46c2f0","tid":1394740,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"同我瘋狂推爆「公務員事務局」FB Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/13946